Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy\Nwhose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe Paramount War against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
