Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.52,0:04:00.49,Title Card - Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.6\fad(1976,1976)\4a&HFF&}A Letter From a Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy, I know. I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too risky to go to Gray Terminal now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're wounded and \Nthere are troops everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--But...!\N--It was a big fire! And chances are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...slim but we all want to believe \Nthat the boss and Ace are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogra went there to look for \Nthem now so trust him and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's having a hard \Ntime - not just you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--The fishing boat has been hit!\N--How's the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He made the Celestial Dragon mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The ship is catching fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they shoot me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Jalmack! There is a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone flies a black flag, he's \Na pirate regardless of who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A commoner shouldn't cross \Nthe path of my ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What was that ship doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an important ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't \Nwanna put the Celestial Dragon in a bad mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the shipwreck already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's severely wounded! \NHurry up and treat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that I was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,--But...!\N--Why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy is just happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you about the night of the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After we left with Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened to you and boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought against Bluejam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And we barely defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we tried to follow you guys right away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fire was blocking our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wait!\N--What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice since I told them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd take responsibility \Nfor bringing you home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my lead. Don't get \Nseparated at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dadan! Are you alright, Dadan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it through the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nbut Dadan got severely burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to get to the riverside \Nin the Middlewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me! You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the town to steal some \Nmedicine and get something to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried to save Dadan's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry \Nabout me so just go, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap! I thought you were \Nresponsible for bringing me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Some survivors could be around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone get away! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, we see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, \NI'm glad that you both survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe what \Nhappened to Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sabo is worrying about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Banzai!\N--Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Another rude commoner could \Nappear at any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--Watch carefully.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how's Sabo doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad that Ace is back \Nand Dadan is recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help getting fired up sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always afraid that if I run,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave something important behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy was behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know but I think that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he faced a cloud \Nof enemies beyond his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger would never run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he suicidal? Running \Naway is a strategy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right but he'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he'd leave the \Npeople he loved behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If he ran, he would put his crew in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, "he wouldn't run \Naway" isn't quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't let the enemy have \Na chance to go after his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd change into a sort of \Ndemon in those situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He once destroyed a country's entire military
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because they talked badly about his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd become violent when angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,\NHe was short-tempered and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was naive and straightforward \Nlike a child at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because his early life was like Ace's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He hated to lose those he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was that reckless but he survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and became the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he got a bad reputation, \Nhis crew trusted him implicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I as a Navy soldier \Ncouldn't help respecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to take care of Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones taking care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Have something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of the world still hate Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And while Ace hates his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it really is "like father, like son."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's see which \None of you will win...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking for Ace and Dadan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?! Sabo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop lying, you fool! \NDon't even joke about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying or joking \Nabout it! It was so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could barely believe what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Sabo went back to his family's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he be at sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! He went home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A hoodlum like me can \Nunderstand how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't always wanna \Ngo back to their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was really happy, \Nhe wouldn't go out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't go out to sea by himself \Nwith a black flag on his ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was all by myself even if I had parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why didn't we go \Nthere to take him back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the guy who killed \NSabo now?! I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kill the Celestial Dragon?! \NThat's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so confident even \Nthough you're not that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do?! They'll just kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die and people will \Nforget you by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a nameless kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo was killed by this country! This world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father changed the world by his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When you become a man that important,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie this fool up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Stop crying like a girl, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to your senses, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--Untie him.\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Where's Luffy?\N--He's been crying all night and he's sleeping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! You're not gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a letter from Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:55.97,"Sign",,0,0,0,,{\an9}"To my brothers at Mt. Corvo\NFrom Sabo"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've sent it before he went out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna go to the town! \NIt's for us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ace, Luffy, I hope you guys \Nweren't hurt in the fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm worrying about you both but \NI believe that you're okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry to say it, guys, but when you \Nget this letter, I'll already be..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"...out on the sea."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Things led to things and I decided \Nto set out to sea before you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"My destination will be anywhere but here."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm gonna become stronger \Nand become a pirate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"The three of us have to become \Nthe freest pirates ever."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"One day, let's meet up again somewhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Somewhere on the wide open sea! \NDefinitely, someday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"By the way, Ace, which of us \Ndo you think is the bigger brother?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Two big brothers and one little brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's odd but our brotherhood \Nis my treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Luffy is still a weak crybaby but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"...he is our little brother \Nso take good care of him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they call themselves \Nobservers?! They're partying everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't covered Sabo's story...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that his parents didn't take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His parents are nobles
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're powerless against the World \NGovernment and Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Luffy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He still isn't eating much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But he still eats twice as much as we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Sabo's death really got to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta set out to sea someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of this \Ncountry and live freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer are you gonna lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure that we were hiding \Nin the forest is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The survivors from Bluejam's crew took \Nit or maybe the military found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't care about the treasure anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the pirate savings that \NI was gonna share with Sabo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but Sabo didn't need it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll just let it go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use having treasure \Nif you can't even protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ace... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,More, and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,More, more and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna become even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can protect anything or anyone! \NI don't have to lose anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Worry about yourself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're far weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo told me to take care of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise that I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I leave a wimpy \Nbrother like you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not smart so I don't quite \Nknow what really killed Sabo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must be something opposed to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo died before he knew freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We exchanged that same cup \Nof sake and we're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys from noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...will become full nobles when they turn 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need to leave here by 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and live as we like. \NFreer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we'll make enemies of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the old man will become our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta risk everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out to sea at 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will become... pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and Ace are stricken with grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but they hold on to their \Ndream of becoming pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and set off toward the future again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Their day of departure will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To achieve the dream that \NSabo was unable to realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"In Order to Keep the Promise \NTheir Separate Departures!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
